dan memihak mereka?

297
00:21:36,609 --> 00:21:37,680
Bagaimana perasaanmu?

298
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,280
Itu akan terasa memalukan.

299
00:21:40,050 --> 00:21:41,079
Kurasa tidak.

300
00:21:42,649 --> 00:21:43,690
Apa maksud Anda?

301
00:21:44,819 --> 00:21:46,290
Kamu akan kecewa.

302
00:21:46,819 --> 00:21:48,589
Sangat kecewa.

303
00:22:00,399 --> 00:22:02,639
"Medali Emas, Han Min Soo"

304
