344
00:24:16,839 --> 00:24:18,409
Dia terbang kembali hari ini.

345
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:33,659
Aku tidak bisa merelakan So Myung.

346
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:36,690
Seperti kita,

347
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:38,790
dia bayi istimewa yang memiliki nama.

348
00:24:41,159 --> 00:24:42,230
So Myung.

349
00:24:44,129 --> 00:24:50,409
"Nama bayi, So Myung"

